response.overview: Jed Clampett and kin move from Arkansas to Beverly Hills when he becomes a billionaire, after an oil strike. The country folk are very naive with regard to life in the big city, so when Jed starts a search for a new wife there are inevitably plenty of takers and con artists ready to make a fast buck
response.tagline: The day they moved in... Beverly Hills moved out.
response.title: The Beverly Hillbillies
